snippet.description:
GAMEJOLT PAGE: https://gamejolt.com/games/PwP/669217
DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.com/invite/7n37yVF5Sk

After the failure of the latest entertainment establishment; Percy's Playhouse. Your boss gives you a call, asking if you can watch over the now defunct play-place until it gets demolished at the end of the week. Fortunately, your PAL Percy isn't letting that happen, and he and his lackeys will make sure of it.

This is the first trailer for Playtime with Percy, a Five Nights at Freddy's based project with a unique "Tamagotchi" twist. This trailer features various cinematic sequences, gameplay shots, and even hints about certain events in-game.

CREDITS:
@FazieFunbear - Editing / Producer / Animator
@lucinadoucheina - Animator / Music
​ @swampmonster6716 - (SoggySoup) - Animator
@purixi4199 - Animator
@RydenW - Models
@Hazel_16 - Models

This trailer uses a custom remix of Dead Man’s Bones' “In The Room Where You Sleep (feat. The Silverlake Conservatory of Music Children’s Choir).” Dead Man’s Bones, Anti-Records, 2009.

